genresAdvancedInfo.name: swedish folk pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre blends the traditional sounds of Swedish folk music with modern pop sensibilities. It features catchy melodies, upbeat rhythms, and often incorporates electronic elements. The lyrics often touch on themes of love, nature, and Swedish culture, making it a popular genre both in Sweden and internationally.
